  "description": "Fresh off its award-winning, sold-out run at the Victoria Fringe, 52 Stories is a storytelling show that takes place inside the memory palace of Pick-of-the-Fringe award-winning storyteller Dave Morris. Come and enjoy some heartwarming and heartbreaking stories of family, friends, love, loss, and of course, memory.",
